Fix use of uninitalized memory. Found by malloc option J.
https://savannah.gnu.org/bugs/index.php?46988

--- engine/engine.c.orig	Tue Mar 25 15:02:25 2014
+++ engine/engine.c	Tue Jan 26 09:03:34 2016
